[h3 id=Introduction 
	" Introduction
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Ninja Gaiden 2 is the sequel to that ninja game where you have to run fast and kill everything to win. In this case, you also need to run fast and kill everything to win.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"This movie was started by Scumtron a while ago, saving 70 frames compared to the currently published movie. The work has continued by eien86, using a bot to analyze all stages of the game to find 4 additional saved frames (plus one 
	[a href=https://tasvideos.org/Forum/Topics/23356#FalseFrames rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"false frame
	]a
	"). 
	$LF
]div
